Name: Star Puzzle
About the game: Star Puzzle-a Classic puzzle for quick thinking and reaction, you need to collect puzzles in a single picture, choosing between the easiest level for beginners, and the most difficult for avid players, who are not afraid of a lot of small details, limited time and number of lives! Game features: - Select the difficulty level - Beautiful Pixel-Art - Convenient control - Puzzles
